## Installation

```bash
# Use without installing (recommended)
npx aem-eds-cli create carousel

# Global install
npm install -g aem-eds-cli
aem-eds create carousel

# Project dev dependency
npm install --save-dev aem-eds-cli
```

---

## Commands

```bash
aem-eds create [block-name]    # Scaffold a new block interactively
aem-eds remove <block-name>    # Delete block folder and all its files
aem-eds list                   # Show all blocks with file status
aem-eds create carousel --dry-run  # Preview without writing files
```

